<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    
    <!-- 
      This is the main Handlebars template for the site 
      - When the user visits the homepage or submits a color the app calls the endpoints in server.js
      - The server script passes data in here and the Handlebars code builds it into the HTML page
    -->
    
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" href="https://glitch.com/favicon.ico" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <title>{{seo.title}}</title>
    
    <!-- Meta tags for SEO and social sharing -->
    <link rel="canonical" href="{{seo.url}}">
    <meta name="description" content="{{seo.description}}">
    <meta property="og:title" content="{{seo.title}}">
    <meta property="og:type" content="article">
    <meta property="og:url" content="{{seo.url}}">
    <meta property="og:description" content="{{seo.description}}">
    <meta property="og:image" content="{{seo.image}}">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary">

    <!-- Import the webpage's stylesheet -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="content" role="main">
        
        <!-- This is the start of content for our page -->
        <h1 class="title">
          <a href="{{ BASE_PAD_URL }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <img src="{{seo.image}}" alt="{{seo.title}}">
          </a>
        </h1>
        
        <div class="color-form">
          
          <p>
            {{seo.description}}
          </p>
          
          <!-- The "What's your favorite color?" form sends a POST request to the server
               Check server.js to see how it works -->
          <form class="color-search" method="post">
            <div class="group">
              <label for="pad-url">
                Quelle est l'adresse du pad&nbsp;?<br>
                <input id="pad-url" size="40" name="url" required pattern="{{ BASE_PAD_URL }}+" type="url" placeholder="{{ BASE_PAD_URL }}/rapport-activite-2020">
              </label>
            </div>
            
            <div class="group">
              <label for="template">
                Modèle de présentation<br>
                <select id="template" required>
                  <option value="default">Modèle par défaut</option>
                </select>
              </label>
            </div>
            
            <div class="group">
              <button type="submit">Transformer en PDF</button>
            </div>
          </form>
          
          <details class="pad-history">
            <summary>Ou, choisis un pad récent auquel tu as accédé…</summary>
            
            <p>
              <a href="https://hackmd.io/s/codimd-configuration">Configurer l'item <code>CMD_ALLOW_ORIGIN</code>
              du CodiMD avec <code>localhost,print-pad.glitch.me</code>
              pour que ça puisse fonctionner.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="links"></div>
      
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
